<table-row><table-column><paragraph-text type="body">Hand-held or like portable drilling machines, e.g. drill guns; Equipment therefor</paragraph-text></table-column><table-column><paragraph-text type="body"><class-ref scheme="cpc">B23B45/00</class-ref></paragraph-text></table-column></table-row>
